::DarkMouse::

She was still looking at her hand. "It...it healed....instantly.....I 
cut it...and it healed...." She couldn't take her eyes off her hand.  
There were no marks or anything on it. It was normal. But she knew 
she had cut it.  There was still a few drops of that fluid on the 
floor. It scared her. She didn't know what it was or what was in her 
body. She sat there shaking.
